Subject: Unable to access the EPP server
Description: Unable to access the EPP server.
What_We_Know__c:
13-05 The customer, ZeMoSo Labs, contacted support because they were unable to access the EPP server, which was causing their CPU usage to hit 100% and preventing access to the dashboard portal.


In the meeting we have uninstall the latest EPP client for Linux and test the CAP policy that was assigned. 

During the session we couldn't observe any slowness or internet access being blocked.
Next_Steps__c:
13-05 We have scheduled the a remote session 

Currently they are monitoring other users to check if any issue reappear
